    <h3 itemprop="headline">Amsterdam celebrates 25 years since the world's first same-sex weddings</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Amsterdam is marking 25 years since the world's first gay marriages were celebrated in the Netherlands.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/04/01/amsterdam-celebrates-25-years-since-the-worlds-first-same-sex-weddings/"  >(Aleksandar Furtula, Mike Corder And Geoff Mulvihill, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
