    <h3 itemprop="headline">Canadian murder suspect on most-wanted list arrested in Mississippi, was in US illegally, DHS says</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Adrian Vincent Walker, one of Canada&apos;s top 25 most wanted fugitives on suspicion of a deadly 2024 Toronto murder., was arrested in Tupelo, Mississippi.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/03/31/canadian-murder-suspect-most-wanted-list-arrested-mississippi-us-illegally-dhs-says/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
