    <h3 itemprop="headline">Air Force F-35 crashes near Las Vegas; pilot survives with minor injuries</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      An F-35 fighter jet crashed near Las Vegas Tuesday, and authorities said the pilot sustained only minor injuries at the Nevada Test &amp; Training Range.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/03/31/air-force-f-35-crashes-near-las-vegas-pilot-survives-minor-injuries/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
