    <h3 itemprop="headline">Florida Supreme Court keeps ex-cop's execution on hold after DNA test fails to give a clear answer</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Florida&apos;s Supreme Court denied a request to lift James Duckett&apos;s execution stay after DNA testing of key evidence came back inconclusive Friday.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/04/01/florida-supreme-court-keeps-ex-cops-execution-hold-dna-test-fails-give-clear-answer/"  >(Fox News)</a>
