    <h3 itemprop="headline">US appeals court denies bid from families of Boeing 737 Max crash victims to reopen criminal case</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A federal appeals court in the United States has denied a request to reopen a criminal case against Boeing tied to two fatal crashes of 737 Max jets.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/03/31/us-appeals-court-denies-bid-from-families-of-boeing-737-max-crash-victims-to-reopen-criminal-case/"  >(Rio Yamat, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
