    <h3 itemprop="headline">Food assistance slashed for hundreds of thousands of Rohingya refugees trapped in Bangladesh camps</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Hundreds of thousands of Rohingya refugees struggling to survive in Bangladesh’s overcrowded camps will see their food assistance slashed.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/04/01/food-assistance-slashed-for-hundreds-of-thousands-of-rohingya-refugees-trapped-in-bangladesh-camps/"  >(Kristen Gelineau, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
