    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">The race against time to destroy Iran&#8217;s illicit nuclear weapons program heats up amid fresh strikes</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The IDF says it struck Iran&apos;s Arak heavy water plant, a key plutonium site, as experts warn Natanz and Isfahan still hold highly enriched uranium.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/03/27/race-against-time-destroy-irans-illicit-nuclear-weapons-program-heats-up-amid-fresh-strikes/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
