        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Iran's war against the US and Israel is being fueled by North Korean weapons, expert warns</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Iran&apos;s ballistic missiles, including the Shahab-3 and Khorramshahr-4, were developed with North Korean help, says expert Bruce Bechtol, who urges stronger sanctions enforcement.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/03/30/irans-war-against-us-israel-being-fueled-north-korean-weapons-expert-warns/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
