    <h3 itemprop="headline">North Korea tests solid-fuel missile engine as Kim boosts threat to US mainland</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Kim Jong Un oversaw a new solid-fuel rocket engine test, state media reports, as North Korea pushes to upgrade its long-range strategic strike capabilities.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/03/29/north-korea-tests-solid-fuel-missile-engine-kim-boosts-threat-us-mainland/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
