      <img src="/static14/world/2026/04/01/chang-ung-north-korean-ex-ioc-member-who-brokered-olympic-joint-marches-with-south-dies.webp" alt="Chang Ung, North Korean ex-IOC member who brokered Olympic joint marches with South, dies" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Chang Ung, North Korean ex-IOC member who brokered Olympic joint marches with South, dies</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Chang Ung, a former North Korean member of the International Olympic Committee who once led sports exchanges with rival South Korea including joint marches of their athletes at the Olympics, has died at 87.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/04/01/chang-ung-north-korean-ex-ioc-member-who-brokered-olympic-joint-marches-with-south-dies/"  >(Hyung-Jin Kim, Associated Press, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
