        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Meta, Snapchat, TikTok and YouTube aren't fully complying with child account ban, Australia says</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Australia is considering bringing court action against Facebook, Instagram, Snapchat, TikTok and YouTube after alleging they are not doing enough to keep Australian children younger than 16 off their platforms.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2026/03/31/meta-snapchat-tiktok-and-youtube-arent-fully-complying-with-child-account-ban-australia-says/"  >(Rod Mcguirk, Associated Press, Local 4)</a>
